{"tid":452062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇死冇事]成立調查組做下樣查吳國際","createTime":"2017-10-29T23:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T14:08:59.000Z","uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6a2a677625b4536a34371aba3feb55cdbf2003","tid":452062,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:18:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1361950-20171029.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1361950-20171029.htm&d=%2B6eTumih%2F5wjI2JwnfYunjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a8f75610\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1361950-20171029.htm&h=01074419\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1361950-20171029.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院委任調查小組調查吳國際手術途中離開事件<br />\n2017-10-29 HKT 23:09<br />\n 分享工具\t facebook  twitter<br />\n 吳國際被指進行肝移植手術期間離開醫院。（港台圖片）<br />\n吳國際被指進行肝移植手術期間離開醫院。（港台圖片）<br />\n港大肝膽胰外科臨床副教授吳國際，被指參與瑪麗醫院一宗屍肝手術期間離開手術室，到另一間私家醫院做手術。瑪麗醫院已委任調查小組調查事件，由該院的副行政總監唐漢軍出任主席。<br />\n<br />\n小組成員包括瑪麗醫院及贊育醫院管治委員會成員勞建青，身兼港大醫學院外科學系主任的瑪麗醫院外科部門主管鄭永強，與港大醫療系統臨床總監雷操奭。<br />\n<br />\n小組將向瑪麗醫院行政總監陸志聰提交報告，以及提出改善建議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n個人簽名 &times;按此隱藏<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\nOct 28近期活躍五毛<br />\n0群龍共舞 1天才小釣手 2三色貓 3JR 4法國佬巫斯義 <br />\n5吾系甘開心牙 6真律師何君堯 7蘇麗珊 8十卜ching <br />\n9D_wade 10RedBaron 11優美開始 12阿古路 13Romanov <br />\n14返六日唔撚易 15優美開始 16民國復興 17dewi <br />\n18侵b 19曼聯明叔 20bb chu 21小翁翁</span>"},{"pid":"5dd1adcdde0b089813afa950d9ecf7ba528ac064","tid":452062,"uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:18:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">賠率<br />\n譴責1:8<br />\n除牌1:99<br />\n冇事封盤</span>"},{"pid":"4d7483681da9902502166b24f0646ff6f2c18e0f","tid":452062,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"「球證、旁證、足協、足總、足委，全部都係我的人，點同我打呀？」"},{"pid":"4bd5bfb3bc30df5674efc68bb82122e51d114ef1","tid":452062,"uid":54079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:30:45.000Z","msg":"難d"},{"pid":"9bdad2f88ac31761a67a35d812bbe6c7b15e5d05","tid":452062,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:32:49.000Z","msg":"都未撚搞著醫委會<br />\n驚閪<br />\n分分鐘醫院需要個醫生多過醫生需要間醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7263a23fcf26d1ae403aad0e5afb071bb4c88e3d","tid":452062,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a9ae749c5912d46de8c2f79c08137950dda553","tid":452062,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:59:45.000Z","msg":"兩年後：判行為失當,停牌一星期<br />\n去個旅行就完咗"},{"pid":"d74481d236395f8d2af66e8d662376a5a4dea3ac","tid":452062,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩年後：判行為失當,停牌一星期<br />\n去個旅行就完咗</blockquote><br />\n呢啲星球人其實除牌都唔係好有野<br />\n都搵夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee28e9fe7b7f1f16cd1b1eec624c8481693d9ec2","tid":452062,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"吳國際點會出國旅行？<br />\nNot International<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155179f51d91ba563486b4b523a012e1c0d8a4c0","tid":452062,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"推到吳生冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6071ff8f99ec760ce69bc68519351cc75420d725","tid":452062,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吳國際點會出國旅行？<br />\nNot International<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"